                  │
┌─────────────────▼───────────────────────────────┐
│             CAPA DE DATOS                        │
├───────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Inicio: Google Sheets (gratuito, simple)        │
│  Escalamiento: Supabase (PostgreSQL free tier)   │
│  ├── members (id, tel, wa_consent, plan)         │
│  ├── checkins (member_id, ts, source, class_id)  │
│  ├── payments (member_id, amount, status, due)   │
│  └── feedback (member_id, rating, comment)       │
